data.description: Elegant two-story residence offering three bedrooms and one bathroom. Ascend the staircase to discover the comfortable bedrooms, while the main floor seamlessly integrates the living areas. Embrace the charm of this well-maintained property that combines practicality and style, providing an ideal backdrop for a cozy and functional lifestyle. The basement has plenty of space with the option to add another bathroom with a toilet already in place. Dry basement ready for you make it your own! Gutter guards installed as well for easy maintenance in the fall!
